en_63823_0	The Southern Province office of the Department for Registration of Persons and the one day service for the issue of National Identity Cards will commence tomorrow.
en_63823_1	It will take place under the patronage of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremasinghe.
en_63823_2	The Southern Provincial Identity Card Office will be opened at the Ground Floor of the Galle Kadawathsathara Divisional Secretariat.
en_63823_3	Minister Vajira Abeywardena said that the Valuation Office and the Passport Office will be opened in Galle in the near future.
en_63823_4	The Prime Minister will also vest in the people the newly constructed Baddegama Divisional Secretariat with the intention of making the public service more efficient.
en_63823_5	The expenditure incurred on it was 87.4 million rupees.
en_63823_6	The building will house a fully-fledged auditorium with a seating capacity of 300 and also a vehicle park.
